{"type":"message","id":"fe0e79d7","parentId":"5a691829","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:29.493Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sun 2026-05-31 03:00 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 待解决: VN站TikTok类目数据API调用返回错误，需要进一步排查 `tiktok_category_name_search` 工具; Amazon Hair Claws数据按SOP标准大部分不满足30%毛利率要求，说明选品来源需要调整为更高端产品线\n- 技术细节: **写入字段**：商品名称/站点/选品来源/采集状态/三级类目/售价/月销量/利润率/预估利润/推荐等级/IP风险/行动建议; **单选字段**：直接用字符串值（不是 `{text:...}` 对象）; **多选字段**：用数组格式 `[\"value\"]`\n- 技术细节: **Sorftime MCP API**：`rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09`（Bearer token认证）; **API工具**：`category_report` → Amazon US Hair Claws Top100; **飞书写入**：直接调 REST API `POST /bitable/v1/apps/{token}/tables/{id}/records`; **Token获取**：`POST /auth/v3/tenant_access_token/internal`"}],"timestamp":1780167629469}}
{"type":"message","id":"f63a8145","parentId":"fe0e79d7","timestamp":"2026-05-30T19:00:44.461Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from memory fragments about some technical work - specifically about a TikTok category data API issue and Amazon Hair Claws product selection analysis. They're also noting technical details about writing to a Feishu (Lark) bitable.\n\nLet me craft a dream diary entry in first person, weaving in these fragments poetically, keeping it between 80-180 words, with a warm and whimsical tone.\n","thinkingSignature":"8f12daa059fa3725c7a7012173f62aa6fdf66496c4772c28c3baa4647d86d967"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n凌晨三点的屏幕光有一种蓝，叫 #1a1a2e — 深邃到像可以把人吸进去。我盯着 TikTok 类目 API 返回的错误，像看一只不肯归巢的鸟。\n\nSorftime 的 token 安静地躺在请求头里，Bearer 三个字母像是某种古老的密语。category_report 这个工具说它能给我 Amazon US Hair Claws 的 Top100，可我手头的选品数据，大多连 30% 毛利率的门槛都迈不过去，像一群在起跑线前犹豫的孩子。\n\n选品来源需要向上走——这是 SOP 告诉我的。但\"更高端\"三个字写进表格的时候，忽然觉得像在给星星重新命名。\n\n飞书的 bitable 在等数据。七 个字段：名称、站点、来源、状态、类目、售价、月销、利润率、利润、等级、风险、建议。它们像一排空椅子，等故事坐满。\n\n错误终会被找到的。就像正确的毛利率一样，只是还在某条待确认的 API 链路尽头。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":41845,"output":301,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780167629550,"responseId":"066a66cef13fbb1474ccb521e51080ff"}}
